  "text": "A simplified version of such strategy, used in the popular Maui scheduler [CITATION_1] , is shown as Algorithm 1, which is also used as the classical backfilling algorithm in our trace-driven simulation experiments. Other popular schedulers such as EASY and LoadLeveler also use similar frameworks.",
